---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "2019 Dirty River Derby";
const pageDescription = "The Dirty River Derby is the rivalry between FC Cincinnati and Louisville City FC, with a history spanning back to 2016. In 2019, FC Cincinnati won the single meeting of the two clubs in the US Open Cup.";

---

<Layout title={title} pageDescription={pageDescription}>
  <main>
    <h1>2019 Dirty River Derby</h1>
    <img src="assets/img/derby_icon.png" alt="Dirty River Derby">

    <h2>June 12th, 2019</h2>
    <p>The one and only meeting this year of the two teams. Louisville entered the battle with 2 DRD wins to Cincy's 1 and an Open Cup history between them. Cincinnati pulled ahead in the 13th minute of extra time securing the win and moving on to the next round of the US Open Cup.</p>

    <h2>Cincinnati Win</h2>
    <img src="/assets/img/logos/fc_cincinnati_2019.svg" alt="FC Cincinnati" class="team-logo">

    <section>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Team</th>
            <th>W</th>
            <th>L</th>
            <th>T</th>
            <th>GD</th>
            <th>Points</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td class="team-name"><img src="/assets/img/logos/fc_cincinnati_2019.svg" alt="" class="team-logo--table"> FC Cincinnati</td>
            <td>1</td>
            <td>0</td>
            <td>0</td>
            <td>1</td>
            <td>3</td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="team-name"><img src="/assets/img/logos/louisville_city.svg" alt="" class="team-logo--table"> Louisville City FC</td>
            <td>0</td>
            <td>1</td>
            <tD>0</tD>
            <td>-1</td>
            <td>0</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h3>2019 Schedule</h3>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr>
            <th>Date</th>
            <th>Location</th>
            <th>Result</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr>
            <td>June 12</td>
            <td>Cincinnati</td>
            <td>2-1</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <p><small>The Dirty River Derby is the <strong>real</strong> name for all Cincinnati/Louisville rivalry games played. The Open Cup match will be the only meeting and therefore the only effect on the standings in 2019.</small></p>
    </section>
    <hr />
    <section>
      <h1>2019 Plastic Cup</h1>

      <h2>- No Plastic Cup this year -</h2>
      <p><small>The Plastic Cup is a Supporters tournament played by the Louisville Coopers and Cincinnati Pride before each installment of the DRD.</small></p>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>
